NG0447:2: dz+nya na dz+wa la b+ha ma la a hi b+ha a /
NG0447:4: ye shes bkod pa rang 'bar ba'o //
NG0447:5: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0447:6: 'di skad bshad pa'i dus gcig na /
NG0447:7: thams cad tha dad med par brdal lo //
NG0447:9: 'byed pa med par mnyam pa'i ngang nyid do //
NG0447:10: rang 'bar ba'i klong 'byed pa med pa'i ngang */
NG0447:11: snang ba med pa'i khyab pa /
NG0447:14: dngos po med pa'i thugs rje /
NG0447:16: rang byung chen po rgyun no //
NG0447:17: dngos po med pa'i snang ba /
NG0447:20: byas pa med pa'i rang shar ro //
NG0447:22: bag chags phung por snang ba 'di //
NG0447:23: zag bcas lus te skye shing snang *//
NG0447:24: dbugs kyi 'gyu ba chad pa la //
NG0447:25: skye shi zhes ni brjod pa yin //
NG0447:26: 'jig rten pa zhes brjod pa yin //
NG0447:27: lta ba chags pa sgom pa 'dod pa'o //
NG0447:28: spyod pa sdug bsngal nges med kyi //
NG0447:32: bag chags lus la nges pa med //
NG0447:33: mya ngan 'das zhes spyod pa yang *//
NG0447:34: lta ba bdag med sgom pa dngos med la //
NG0447:35: dkar po spyad pa bdag gzhan don du spyod //
NG0447:36: skye rgas na 'chi'i chu bo bzhi las kyang *//
NG0447:38: ting 'dzin khyad par nges pa med //
NG0447:39: sems kyi snying po kun gzhi khyab chen la //
NG0447:40: tha dad tshig gi sgo nas phye na gnyis //
NG0447:41: phyi rol mu stegs nang pa sangs rgyas pa //
NG0447:42: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag sprin ltar ro //
NG0447:43: 'khor ba'i chos ni sdug bsngal tshe 'byung 'dra //
NG0447:44: dngos por snang ba stong ste chu gzugs par //
NG0447:45: gzung 'dzin chos la bdag med nyi zer @#//
NG0447:47: de ltar shes shing rtogs na nang pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NG0447:48: ma rtogs rtag chad mtha' la zhen na phyi rol mu stegs pa'o //
NG0447:49: mu stegs chos la lta na grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:50: bsdu na rtag chad de gnyis so //
NG0447:51: rtag par 'dod pa'i lta ba grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:52: bsdu na bdag rtag dngos po'i chos su grub //
NG0447:53: skad cig gnyis par mi 'gyur don byed bdag nyid can //
NG0447:54: de la rdo rje sems dpas brjod pa yang *//
NG0447:55: rig pa byang chub sems nyid klong yangs 'di //
NG0447:56: rgyu rkyen med pa'i ye shes 'od re gsal //
NG0447:57: dngos po med pa'i rig pa 'od zer 'phro //
NG0447:58: de la bdag tu lta ba'i gang zag e ma 'khrul //
NG0447:60: mu stegs chad pa'i lta ba grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:61: bsdus na tshe 'di snga phyi med pa'i blo bur ba //
NG0447:62: las la dge sdig med la chos la rgyu 'bras med //
NG0447:63: dper na la khar me shi thal ba rlung khyer bzhin //
NG0447:64: sangs rgyas 'dod na bskal bar tshogs bsags dgos //
NG0447:65: blo bur tshe la bskal ba'i tha snyad med //
NG0447:66: des na sangs rgyas chos dang brdzun du snang *//
NG0447:67: de la rdo rje sems dpas brjod pa //
NG0447:68: tshe nyid sngun ma yin pa'i gtan tshigs yin //
NG0447:69: bu chung mdangs skyes nu ma 'thung ba de //
NG0447:70: sngun ma 'asngon du song ba'i bag chags yin //
NG0447:71: sngon dus song glo bur yongs gyur na //
NG0447:72: sa rdo rnams la shes pa skye bar rigs //
NG0447:73: shes pa phyi ma 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs ni //
NG0447:74: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NG0447:75: phyug stogs skyid sdug nges med spyod pa yis //
NG0447:76: phyi ma 'byung ba ngas pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NG0447:77: phyi ma mi 'byung skyid sdug spyod 'gyur na //
NG0447:78: nam mkha'i sprin yang skyid sdug yod par nges //
NG0447:79: ci phyir zhes ni spyod gyur na //
NG0447:80: nam mkha'i sprin yang blo bur 'byung ba yin zhes so //
NG0447:81: de nas kun tu bzang pos brjod pa //
NG0447:82: sems la dngos po med pas 'das pa'i sangs rgyas yin //
NG0447:83: rgyu rkyen med pa rang byung da lta'i sangs rgyas yin //
NG0447:84: gnyen po med pa rang byung ma byon sangs rgyas yin //
NG0447:85: snga phyi thog mtha' med pas brdal ba chos nyid klong *//
NG0447:86: 'pho 'gyur 'jig 'bral med pas dus gsum sangs rgyas sku //
NG0447:87: blun rmongs spyod log khyed la rangs sangs thabs kyis chos //
NG0447:89: ye shes bkod pa rang 'bar ba las /
NG0447:90: tha snyad rtsod pa'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NG0447:91: de nas de bzhin gshegs pas chos thams cad sgro 'dogs gcod pa 'dis gsungs so //
NG0447:92: ye nas snying po dbyer med la //
NG0447:93: theg pa thams cad gnyis su 'dus //
NG0447:94: sgro skur thams cad ye shes dbyings su grol //
NG0447:95: shes rab che ste chos nyid klong du 'byam //
NG0447:96: snying rje chos te phyogs ris med //
NG0447:97: de ltar shes shing rtogs na theg pa chen po yin //
NG0447:98: gang zag sems nyid stong par rtogs //
NG0447:99: chos kyi bdag nyid phyi rol stong par rtogs //
NG0447:100: de ltar shes shing rtogs na theg pa chen po'o //
NG0447:103: 'phags pa nyan thos lta ba grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:104: mthong spangs dang ni sgom spangs gnyis su 'dus //
NG0447:105: mthong spangs phyi ni snang ba 'di //
NG0447:106: rags pa med de phra rab rdul //
NG0447:108: sil bur gnas te ne sing tshul //
NG0447:112: gzung bya phra rags rdul cha la //
NG0447:114: nyi ma dang ni nyi zer dang *//
NG0447:115: skam pa dang ni sla nga 'o //
NG0447:116: yin ni snang dag rig pa'o //
NG0447:117: nyan thos spyad pa bstan pa yang *//
NG0447:118: lus ni chos bdun sgo nas yang *//
NG0447:119: sgyu ma'i zas rnams khad kyis bri //
NG0447:120: nyan thos sgom pa bstan pa yang *//
NG0447:121: dbugs kyi rgyu ba nang du 'then //
NG0447:122: yid kyi rgyu ba rgyun bcad la //
NG0447:123: sna rtser hu~m la shes pa gtad //
NG0447:124: mi g.yo ba yi ting nge 'dzin //
NG0447:125: rang rgyal lta ba bstan pa yang *//
NG0447:126: phyi rol gdul bya logs na med //
NG0447:128: rig pa phyi mas sngon ma bzung *//
NG0447:129: dper na nyi 'od nyi zer bzhin //
NG0447:130: tha dad 'dod pa ma yin no //
NG0447:131: sgom dang spyod pa sngar dang mthun //
NG0447:132: rdo rje sems dpas brjod pa //
NG0447:133: phyi rol sems kyi rtsal snang la //
NG0447:134: sgyu mar rtogs kyis rmongs pa khyod //
NG0447:136: gzung med 'dzin pas nor pa yin //
NG0447:137: don la med pas log pa yin //
NG0447:138: dper na smig sgyu bsnyeg pa 'dra //
NG0447:139: ye shes bkod pa rang 'bar ba las //
NG0447:140: gnyis su med par bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o //
NG0447:141: de nas bde bar gshegs pas 'bras bu gnyis su med pa 'di brjod do //
NG0447:142: theg pa chen po dbyer med gnyis su bsdus //
NG0447:143: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang *//
NG0447:145: the tshom thams cad chos kyi dbyings su grol //
NG0447:146: sems la sangs rgyas 'byung bar 'dod na rgyu yi theg pa yin //
NG0447:147: sems nyid 'gyur ba med par rtogs na 'bras bu'i theg pa'o //
NG0447:148: kun rdzob snang ba spang byar 'dod na mtshan nyid theg pa'o //
NG0447:149: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med rang shar 'bras bu'i theg pa'o //
NG0447:150: mtshan nyid theg pa dbu ma sems tsam bshad //
NG0447:151: sems tsam lta ba grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:152: sems tsam rnam par bden pa dang *//
NG0447:153: sems tsam rnam par rdzun pa dang *//
NG0447:154: sgo lnga rtsal ba lta ba gsum //
NG0447:155: kha dog du ma cir snang kyang *//
NG0447:156: shes pa cha med ngo bor yang *//
NG0447:157: 'khor 'das thams cad byang chub sems su gsal //
NG0447:158: de yang rang rig gsal ba myong ba med //
NG0447:159: snang ba sna tshogs cir snang yang *//
NG0447:160: rang rig rang gsal cha med ngo bor gcig / sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul cir snang yang *//
NG0447:161: rang rig rang gsal brjod med ngo bor gcig / kha dog dkar dmar cir gsal yang *//
NG0447:163: rang rig rang gsal cha med @#//
NG0447:165: kun gzhi stong pa'i rtsal shar yin //
NG0447:166: rang rig lta ba'i rmongs pa khyod //
NG0447:167: rig par 'dod na sdug bsngal rgyu //
NG0447:168: gsal bar 'dod na ngan song ltung *//
NG0447:170: rang rig rgyal po phyogs med grol //
NG0447:172: dbu ma'i lta ba grangs med kyang *//
NG0447:173: tshe med tshe men ston men gsum //
NG0447:174: don dam 'dod pa spros pa'i mtha' brgyad bral //
NG0447:175: yod mtha' med mtha' snang mtha' stong mtha' dang *//
NG0447:176: gnyis ka'i mtha' dang gnyis ka ma yin mtha' //
NG0447:177: gcig dang du ma'i mtha' dang bral //
NG0447:178: de ni bsgrub bya yongs gcod don dam 'dod pa'o //
NG0447:179: kun rdzob 'dod pa rnam gnyis log pa'i kun rdzob dpe brgyad do //
NG0447:180: sab mo ltar mthong smig sgyu chur mthong dang *//
NG0447:181: thag pa sprul mthong tho yor mir mthong dang *//
NG0447:182: nam mkha' skra 'dzag rmi lam longs spyod dang *//
NG0447:183: rgya mtsho'i chu gzugs nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon rnams //
NG0447:184: med par snang bas log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NG0447:185: yang dag kun rdzob gang yin pa'i //
NG0447:187: rkyen las skyes la don byed nus //
NG0447:188: mthun par snang la brtags na dben //
NG0447:189: chos sku'i rtsal dang ye shes 'od kyi rkyen las skyes //
NG0447:190: sems can las kyi spyi mthun don byed nus //
NG0447:191: lha la bdud rtsi lha min go mtshon dang *//
NG0447:192: mi la sa rdo byol song ngam grog dang *//
NG0447:193: yi dwags rnag khrag dmyal ba me chur snang *//
NG0447:194: de yang gcig snang ma yin tha dad par re snang *//
NG0447:195: de yang chos sku'i rtsal la ye shes 'od //
NG0447:196: sems kyi bkrag shar rig pa'i yul yin pas //
NG0447:197: de nas thams cad brtags na dben pa'o //
NG0447:198: de yang dgag bya rnam gcod kun rdzob 'dod pa'o //
NG0447:199: rdo rje sems dpa' brjod pas //
NG0447:200: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med thams cad rang shar la //
NG0447:201: tha dad phyogs ris byed pa e ma rmongs pa 'khrul //
NG0447:202: thams cad chos dbyings 'gyur med brdal ba la //
NG0447:203: spros pa'i mtha' brgyad 'dod pa e ma rmongs pa gol //
NG0447:204: chos sku gting gsal ye shes klong yangs la //
NG0447:205: don dam kun rdzob dgag sgrub 'dod pa e ma
NG0447:206: rmongs pa mchog / chos sku kun gzhi rmongs pa
NG0447:208: khas mi len gyi lta ba e ma rmongs pa 'khrul //
NG0447:210: ye shes bkod pa rang 'bar ba'i rgyud las //
NG0447:211: dbyer med par sun dbyung ba'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NG0447:212: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NG0447:214: skyon yon thams cad chos nyid klong du grol //
NG0447:215: 'bras bu rdo rje theg pa gnyis su bshad //
NG0447:216: phyi sa thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang *//
NG0447:217: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NG0447:218: lta ba thams cad rang byung ye shes chen por gsal //
NG0447:219: sgom pa thams cad phyogs tshigs med pas spyan ras gzigs //
NG0447:220: snang ba dngos po med pas 'jam dpal nyid //
NG0447:223: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su med par brdal //
NG0447:224: gtsang dang 'jigs pa'i brtul zhugs drag par spyod //
NG0447:225: 'du 'bral med pa'i ting nge 'dzin rang grol shar //
NG0447:226: 'gro ba'i don la thugs rje'i sbyor ba brtson //
NG0447:227: u pa ya nyid bdag gzhan mtha' yas 'das //
NG0447:228: don dam rnam dag chos nyid spros dang bral //
NG0447:229: 'byed pa med pa'i ting 'dzin phyogs dang bral //
NG0447:230: kun dzob rigs bzhi rdo rje 'bar ba 'phro //
NG0447:231: snang ba spyan ras stong pa 'jam //
NG0447:232: dbyer med phyag rdor rang grol rnam snang nyid //
NG0447:233: bden pa gnyis med thams cad rang shar 'bar //
NG0447:234: bde ba'i rgyal po ye shes 'bar ba'i gtso //
NG0447:235: yo ga'i lta spyod 'gro nyid ni //
NG0447:236: rnam par dag pa'i chos nyid rdul dang bral //
NG0447:237: blta ru med pa'i ting 'dzin nyams dang ldan //
NG0447:238: spyad du med pa'i rtsol bas bde ba 'byin //
NG0447:239: kun rdzob sangs rgyas rdza mo rlags pa tsam //
NG0447:240: mi mngon dbyings nas gnyis su med par zhugs //
NG0447:241: 'gro ba'i don la thugs rje rgya ma chad //
NG0447:242: ris dang sku mdog phyag mtshan nges med sna tshogs
NG0447:243: snang *// gnyis su med pa'i sbyor bas khams gsum 'khor ba 'dren //
NG0447:244: rdo rje sems dpa' brjod pas //
NG0447:245: ye nas snying po dbyer med bde ba chen po la //
NG0447:246: don dam kun rdzob bzang rtog lta ba rmongs pa 'khrul //
NG0447:247: ye shes chos dbyings chen pos brdal khyab 'bar ba la //
NG0447:248: gnyis su med pa'i thus rje skye bo rmongs pa gol //
NG0447:249: ye nas stong nyid klong chen 'byal pa la //
NG0447:250: gtsang dang lhar lta rmongs pa e ma 'khrul //
NG0447:252: gsang ba bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi 'gro nyid do //
NG0447:253: skyon thams cad chos nyid klong du grol //
NG0447:254: grub mtha' thams cad bskyed rdzogs gsum du 'dus //
NG0447:255: re dogs thams cad ye shes klong du grol //
NG0447:256: gzhi ni sems nyid stong gsal la //
NG0447:257: snang ba lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor chen por
NG0447:258: dag / sems nyid rtsal snang thabs dang shes rab
NG0447:259: 'du 'bral med // snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor la rang grol dbyings su dag pa dang *//
NG0447:260: rig pa'i che 'phrul dbyings dbang dang ye shes 'gyur med bde bar lta //
NG0447:261: snang ba phyogs ris thams cad dang bral //
NG0447:262: snang bzhin mi gnas ngo bo nyid //
NG0447:263: rig pa rang snang thams cad 'gyur med klong chen brdal //
NG0447:264: dper na rgyal po rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul nyid do //
NG0447:265: ma ha yo ga bde chen ngang las grol //
NG0447:266: snang stong dbyer med byang chub sems la rdzogs //
NG0447:267: thabs ni snang ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor la //
NG0447:268: shes rab thams cad stong gsal sems su rdzogs //
NG0447:269: bde ba chen po thugs kyi dkyil du 'bar //
NG0447:270: shes rab chen pos rtogs tshod lha ru dag /
NG0447:271: ting 'dzin rgyal pos stong gsal chen por dag /
NG0447:272: u nu bde ba chen pos rang grol bas //
NG0447:273: snang ba thams cad dbyings kyi klaung du grol //
NG0447:274: gsal ba thams cad ye shes ngang du dag / rig pa thams @#//
NG0447:275: cad bde ba chen por shar //
NG0447:276: ting 'dzin thams cad rtsol sgrub med par dag / spyod pa thams cad rang sangs chen por grol //
NG0447:277: lta ba thams cad rgya yan chen por 'byams //
NG0447:278: re dog thams cad chos nyid ngang du 'byam //
NG0447:279: skyon yon thams cad rang byung klong du dag / zag med bde ba'i ngang du thams cad rdzogs //
NG0447:280: de la rdo rje sems dpas brjod pas //
NG0447:281: chos sku 'gyur med ye shes 'gyur med chen po la //
NG0447:283: chos dbyings klong chen mu mtha' yas pa la //
NG0447:284: 'du 'bral med pa 'dod pa e ma bdag re gol //
NG0447:285: ye shes snying po gting gsal 'gyur med la //
NG0447:286: lta sgom sems nyid rtog pa e ma rmongs pa log / ces brjod do //
NG0447:287: rdzogs chen a ti kun gyi dngos gzhir shar //
NG0447:288: dngos med rang byung nam mkha'i bya lam 'dra //
NG0447:289: gting gsal 'gyur med nam mkha'i gdangs dang 'dra //
NG0447:290: ma spros brdal khyab nam mkha'i mtha' dang 'dra //
NG0447:291: ma ltas ye gsal nam mkha'i dbyings dang 'dra //
NG0447:292: ma skyes ye rdzogs nam mkha'i klong dang 'dra //
NG0447:293: ye shes bkod pa rang 'bar ba las //
NG0447:294: gsang sngags bcud phyung ba'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NG0447:295: de nas bde bar gshegs pas yang dag 'di brjod do //
NG0447:296: mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:297: mi gnas pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:299: mi bskyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:300: mi srong ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:301: mi mnyam pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:302: mi dmigs pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:303: mi byed pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang *//
NG0447:305: snang ba chos sku'i rang 'od las //
NG0447:306: chags zhen thams cad rol pa chen por shar //
NG0447:307: dngos po thams cad chos sku'i rtsal snang la //
NG0447:308: 'dod pa thams cad byang chub chen por shar //
NG0447:309: dbang po lnga nyid ye shes lam chen la //
NG0447:310: shar ba thams cad rang grol chen por shar //
NG0447:311: rig pa thams cad rang byung ye shes la //
NG0447:312: sdug bsngal thams cad ye shes rol par shar //
NG0447:313: chos sku 'gyur ba med pa la //
NG0447:314: skye shi thams cad stong nyid ngang du 'jams //
